                                <div class="phototagleft">
                                  
                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong>Emiley White</strong> is an English (writing) and professional writing dual-degree senior at the University of Oklahoma, a <em>WLT</em> intern, and former assistant editor on the <em>OU Daily</em> engagement desk. When she’s not writing, you'll likely catch her burning up the local library's reading charts or training for a half-marathon.</p>

                                            <div class="clear"></div>
                                                          
